# Relabeller resolution cache (~65MB) + per-entry proposal (~2MB, >500KB limit) — regenerable from arXiv/DataCite/OpenAlex
results/reviewer_experiments/relabel_resolution_cache.json
results/reviewer_experiments/relabel_proposal.json

# btu v1.2.0 regen working dir (~92MB SQLite caches / raw; regenerable). Contents are
# ignored EXCEPT the two released per-entry verdict dumps below, which back the paper's
# bibtex-updater numbers (dev DR 0.865 / FPR 0.092, test 0.877 / 0.115) and let readers
# recompute them offline without re-installing the tool or re-querying external databases.
results/relabel_delta/btu_v1_2_0/*
!results/relabel_delta/btu_v1_2_0/bibtexupdater_dev_public_per_entry.jsonl
!results/relabel_delta/btu_v1_2_0/bibtexupdater_test_public_per_entry.jsonl
